# magento

A Puppet module to install and configure Magento and its dependencies.

We're using it in production, but that doesn't necessarily mean you should ;)

Currently you need to use my fork of James Fryman's nginx module for this:
https://github.com/bashtoni/puppet-nginx/tree/conditionals

